32:39.792 --> 32:42.833
'a productive citizen
if you cooperate.'

32:42.917 --> 32:47.833
'Resistance will be punished.
Cooperation will be rewarded.'

32:50.292 --> 32:51.458
Good morning.

33:08.125 --> 33:12.375
I should tell you that
unless you begin to cooperate

33:12.458 --> 33:16.333
you won't be receiving
any more intravenous nutrition.

33:21.292 --> 33:24.083
It's bad enough they had me
take you off solid food.

33:26.042 --> 33:28.458
Don't compound
the error further.

33:36.458 --> 33:37.833
That piece of paper..

33:39.667 --> 33:41.917
...and a few words
from you are all

33:42.000 --> 33:44.833
that's standing
between you and that door.

33:47.250 --> 33:49.333
'Don't you see
how foolish this is?'

33:50.833 --> 33:53.875
I'm not keeping you here.

33:53.958 --> 33:56.625
They're not keeping you here.
You're keeping you here.

33:58.208 --> 34:02.167
And are you suicidal
or simply self-destructive

34:02.250 --> 34:05.250
preferring to let us
do the work for you?

34:13.208 --> 34:14.750
Don't you want to leave?

34:16.042 --> 34:17.792
'Don't you want to be free?'

34:19.042 --> 34:21.167
Walk through that door?

34:21.250 --> 34:23.875
Feel the sun on your face again?

34:26.250 --> 34:30.542
- Yes.
- 'Then sign it and speak.'

34:30.625 --> 34:33.708
'That's all. Then you can go.'

34:36.042 --> 34:38.792
They don't want you dead.

34:38.875 --> 34:41.708
They want you as a symbol,
not a martyr.

34:41.792 --> 34:44.250
As a warning to others.

34:44.333 --> 34:47.000
- Then you'll kill me.
- No.

34:48.542 --> 34:50.292
Absolutely not.

34:53.583 --> 34:56.583
I told you
I won't lie to you.

34:58.083 --> 35:01.333
No, they'll come
for you eventually.

35:01.417 --> 35:06.000
But they'll wait
until you've been forgotten.

35:06.083 --> 35:10.167
'Until your fate no longer
means anything to anyone.'

35:10.250 --> 35:13.792
They'll come in the night.
It will be very quick.

35:13.875 --> 35:15.667
But until that time..

35:17.500 --> 35:19.417
...you will have your freedom.

35:20.833 --> 35:24.042
If anything,
they'll encourage you to travel

35:24.125 --> 35:26.875
so that more people
can see you as..

35:26.958 --> 35:30.792
...as a symbol of the
pre-eminent truth of our time..

35:32.125 --> 35:34.875
...that you cannot
beat the system.

35:36.500 --> 35:39.042
'I'm telling you the truth.'

35:39.125 --> 35:45.708
'Sign and speak,
and you can leave here.'

35:45.792 --> 35:48.042
It's really that simple.

35:58.292 --> 36:00.292
'I know you can do it.'

36:01.625 --> 36:03.833
'I know you want to do it.'

36:07.500 --> 36:09.208
Well?

36:24.958 --> 36:26.167
No.

36:33.667 --> 36:34.833
I..

36:36.375 --> 36:40.000
I really wish you hadn't done
that, captain.

36:40.083 --> 36:41.500
I really..

36:43.833 --> 36:45.583
...sincerely wish..

36:48.208 --> 36:50.042
...you hadn't done that.

36:54.958 --> 36:56.750
I, I..

36:59.042 --> 37:01.667
I have no control over
what will happen next.

37:04.250 --> 37:06.208
It's out of my hands.

37:19.625 --> 37:22.500
[dramatic music]

37:24.833 --> 37:27.458
Right.
Now, listen to me. Wake up.

37:27.542 --> 37:31.708
There's something
you have to understand. Focus.

37:31.792 --> 37:34.000
Focus on me.

37:34.083 --> 37:37.167
Do you know why
they're doing this to you?

37:37.250 --> 37:39.542
Because you're a war hero,
one of the few to come out

37:39.625 --> 37:41.000
'of the Minbari War.'

37:41.083 --> 37:43.833
They've invested a considerable
amount of time and effort

37:43.917 --> 37:46.333
making you a hero
in the public's eye.

37:48.042 --> 37:51.417
The problem is, when a war hero
starts believing certain things

37:51.500 --> 37:54.833
and saying certain things,
the public listens.

37:54.917 --> 37:57.167
They figure maybe
there's something to it.

37:57.250 --> 38:02.500
Your credibility has become
a threat to their credibility.

38:02.583 --> 38:04.542
So one of them has to go.

38:08.250 --> 38:12.583
The best way out for everyone
is for you to confess

38:12.667 --> 38:14.125
and lay the blame
for what's happened

38:14.208 --> 38:15.625
'at the feet
of the alien government.'

38:15.708 --> 38:17.250
'Whether it's true or not,
it doesn't matter.'

38:17.333 --> 38:19.417
'Truth is immaterial.
They can sell it.'

38:19.500 --> 38:20.958
And they will let you live.

38:21.042 --> 38:23.667
Note,
I said, it is the best way.

38:23.750 --> 38:26.250
I did not say,
it was the only way.

38:30.167 --> 38:35.125
The other way, captain,
is a Posthumous Confession.

38:35.208 --> 38:38.500
Your signature is not a problem.
They have your image on file.

38:38.583 --> 38:42.000
They can create you
reading the confession.

38:42.083 --> 38:44.208
Now, that's not as good
as having you where people

38:44.292 --> 38:46.583
can see you,
so they know it's true that

38:46.667 --> 38:49.375
even you can be broken,
you cannot resist.

38:49.458 --> 38:52.375
With a video record,
there will always be doubt.

38:53.792 --> 38:56.917
It's not the same
as breaking you

38:57.000 --> 38:59.375
but I'm told that
as of this morning..

39:04.500 --> 39:07.625
...it is an acceptable option.

39:13.375 --> 39:16.417
I can save your life.

39:16.500 --> 39:18.333
Right now.

39:20.125 --> 39:21.792
If you'll let me.

39:24.417 --> 39:27.750
You know, it's funny.

39:27.833 --> 39:31.333
I was thinking about
what you said.

39:31.417 --> 39:36.417
The pre-eminent truth
of our age is that you cannot

39:36.500 --> 39:39.167
fight the system.

39:39.250 --> 39:40.792
[scoffs]

39:40.875 --> 39:45.042
But if, as you say,
the truth is fluid

39:45.125 --> 39:48.667
that the truth is subjective..

39:48.750 --> 39:51.833
...then maybe
you can fight the system..

39:51.917 --> 39:56.583
...as long as just one person
refuses to be broken

39:56.667 --> 40:00.375
refuses...to bow down.

40:01.833 --> 40:03.917
But can you win?

40:05.417 --> 40:09.625
Every time I say no.

40:21.917 --> 40:24.917
Captain John Sheridan,
will you or will you not

40:25.000 --> 40:28.958
sign a confession and endorse it
before a public hearing?

40:31.750 --> 40:33.500
No.

40:36.875 --> 40:38.875
[dramatic music]

40:44.958 --> 40:46.625
[grunting]

40:50.958 --> 40:53.208
Do you understand that
this is your last chance?

40:53.292 --> 40:57.625
Do you understand that
this is your very last chance?

41:01.417 --> 41:02.792
Room 17.

41:08.583 --> 41:11.500
Almighty God, look upon your
servant lying in great weakness

41:11.583 --> 41:13.375
and comfort him,
deliver him from all evil

41:13.458 --> 41:15.208
and set him free
from every bond.

41:15.292 --> 41:18.167
No man lives to himself,
and no man dies to himself.

41:18.250 --> 41:21.583
If we live, we live unto God.
If we die, we die unto God.

41:21.667 --> 41:23.542
Therefore into your hands,
we commend your servant

41:23.625 --> 41:26.208
a sheep of your own fold,
a lamb of your own flock.

41:26.292 --> 41:28.208
Receive him into the arms
of your mercy.

41:28.292 --> 41:30.500
May his soul rest in peace.
Amen.

